## Cost of Running the System

This section provides an estimated monthly cost for deploying and running the Grave Management System in a production environment. Actual costs may vary depending on usage, scale, and infrastructure choices.

 

### 1. Hosting (Frontend)

- Platform: Hosgtinger
- Estimated Cost: $7/month  

 

### 2. Backend & Database (Supabase)

- Services:
  - PostgreSQL Database  
  - Authentication  
  - APIs  
- Estimated Cost:Basic Plan free being used ,  $25/month (Pro Plan)  

 

### 3. Automation (n8n)

- Option 1: Self-hosted (recommended)
  - Hosting (VPS): $10/month  being used.
- Option 2: n8n Cloud
  - Cost: $20+/month  

 

### 4. Domain & DNS

- Domain name: $15/year  
- DNS (Cloudflare): Free  

 

### 6. AI Chatbot (Optional Cost)

-  using OpenAI:
  - Estimated Cost: $5 – $20/month (based on usage)  



### Estimated Total Monthly Cost

| Setup Type        | Estimated Cost |
|      |     |
| Minimum Setup    | ~ $20     |

 

### Notes

- Costs increase with:
  - Number of users  
  - Database size  
  - Email volume  
  - AI usage  

- Self-hosting automation (n8n) significantly reduces cost.

 


 

## Summary

The ICSJ Grave Management System is designed to be cost-efficient and scalable. A fully functional production system can be deployed at a relatively low monthly cost, making it suitable for small to large Islamic centers.
